---

<footer class="bg-[#120d08] border-t border-border-dark pt-16 pb-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 lg:px-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white">
          <div class="size-6 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">music_note</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-white text-lg font-bold">FlySky Guitar</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Chế tác tương lai của âm thanh qua từng sợi dây. Hãy gia nhập cộng đồng những nghệ sĩ chọn FlySky.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Cửa hàng</h4>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Guitar Điện</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Guitar Acoustic</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Guitar Bass</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Phụ kiện</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Hỗ trợ</h4>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-text-muted text-sm">
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Thông tin bảo hành</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Giao hàng &amp; Trả hàng</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Hướng dẫn bảo quản</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Liên hệ chúng tôi</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Đăng ký nhận tin</h4>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-4">Đăng ký để nhận thông tin về các mẫu mới nhất và tiêu điểm nghệ sĩ.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <input class="bg-card-dark border border-border-dark text-white text-sm rounded-lg px-4 py-2 w-full focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none" placeholder="Email của bạn" type="email" />
          <button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-background-dark font-bold rounded-lg px-4 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">send</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-border-dark pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm text-center md:text-left">© 2024 FlySky Guitar. Bảo lưu mọi quyền.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#"><span class="sr-only">Facebook</span>FB</a>
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#"><span class="sr-only">Instagram</span>IG</a>
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#"><span class="sr-only">Twitter</span>TW</a>
        <a class="text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#"><span class="sr-only">YouTube</span>YT</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
